data.description: Don't miss out on your opportunity to own this adorable cape cod which is perfectly placed in sought-after South Lebanon Township. Conveniently located between Wellspan Hospital, South Hills Park and the VA Hospital campus, this cozy home has been freshly painted and features new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the main living area. There are two bedrooms on the first floor and an extra large bedroom with bonus reading nook area surrounding the stairs with storage all around. The full basement has been improved with some drywall and flooring and could be used for many purposes for additional living space. (family room, craft room, play room, etc) The back yard is flat and fully fenced and includes a wooden patio and a shed for additional outdoor storage. In the rear of the property off of Plum St is where you will park and/or have a workshop in your oversized 2 car detached garage with a new roof leading into the back yard. Don't delay, schedule your appointment to view today!
